        "custom_liquid": "<div>\n<center><H3 style=\"font-size:28px;font-family: Moneta; line-height:40px;\">Carbon38 was born from an innovative idea, a spontaneous contest entry, a fake website, and 14 post-it notes.<\/h3><br><h2 style=\"font-size:100px; line-height:80px;\">\nToday, we are—\n<\/div>",
