    "about-us-years": {
      "type": "about-us-years",
      "blocks": {
        "year_6jgUJ6": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2011",
            "year": "2011",
            "description": "<p>In November, Katie Warner Johnson attended the Women 2.0 Startup weekend and purchased our URL—www.carbon38.com.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_mHwe9y": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2012",
            "year": "2012",
            "description": "<p>In January, we launched the official Carbon38 Instagram. <\/p><p>Wondering why we posted a picture of Tilapia? Same.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_XXMpMA": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2013",
            "year": "2013",
            "description": "<p>In January, we started conducting business from a one-bedroom apartment and hired our first employee.<\/p><p><\/p><p>In July, we began fundraising.<\/p><p><\/p><p>In September, we received our first check for $100K from the Winklevosss Twins—yes, <em>those<\/em> twins.<\/p><p><\/p><p>In November, we launched as an E-commerce site focusing only on activewear. <\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_t98VdD": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2014",
            "year": "2014",
            "description": "<p>In February, we brought our total fundraising to $1 million.<\/p><p><\/p><p>In September, we leased an office in West Hollywood with desks and computers for all 9 employees.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_wmbxcc": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2015",
            "year": "2015",
            "description": "<p>In September, we started our Series Seed fundraising, raising $11 million.<\/p><p><\/p><p>In November, we launched the first exclusive Carbon38 Branded Label Collection—a mix of active, elevated basics, and signature prints.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_CMNnUE": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2016",
            "year": "2016",
            "description": "<p>In August, our exclusive Takara Shine was born (to date, we’ve sold over 500,000 pairs).<\/p><p>In November, we hit the other coast and opened a pop-up shop on Los Angeles’ famous Roberston Blvd.<\/p><p>In December, we launched our first collaboration with \"Love Me\" artist, Curtis Kulig.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_bcRgV3": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2017",
            "year": "2017",
            "description": "<p>In January, we partnered with award-winning designer Jonathan Simkhai for our second collaboration.<\/p><p><\/p><p>In March, we launched our first line of ready-to-wear pieces—<em>The Met Collection.<\/em><\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_NnCnW7": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2018",
            "year": "2018",
            "description": "<p>In January, a new investor contributed $15 million.<\/p><p>In December, we grew up and moved to our Culver City offices.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_bkfq6R": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2019",
            "year": "2019",
            "description": "<p>We made a name for ourselves in the world of luxury fashion, partnering with a new wave of high-end labels and designers.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_wce7Fx": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2020",
            "year": "2020",
            "description": "<p>In March, the global pandemic began.<\/p><p><\/p><p>We sold our Culver City offices, set up shop as a remote team, and threw ourselves into learning how we could best serve our customers and community. <\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_C9TA3x": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2021",
            "year": "2021",
            "description": "<p>In March, we partnered with Girls Inc, of Greater Los Angeles.<\/p><p><\/p><p>In August, we launched a collaboration with EleVen by Venus Williams—our first tennis collection.<\/p><p><\/p><p>In September, we re-platformed to Shopify.<\/p><p><\/p><p>In October, we partnered with the Breast Cancer Research Foundation to raise funds for the world's most promising research and awareness campaigns. <\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_CCWWaY": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "IT'S TIME FOR SOMETHING NEW",
            "title": "2022",
            "year": "2022",
            "description": "<p>In March, we announced our rebranding, including a new logo, a new feel, and a new us.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "year_x4jTzr": {
          "type": "year",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "2024",
            "year": "2024",
            "description": "<p>By recognizing the potential and success of e-commerce and retail collaborations, BC Brands has acquired Carbon38, ushering in an exciting new era in activewear.<\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
